    dc:description "Fig. 2. (A) Apodrosus epipolevatus, head, ventral view; (B) A. argentatus, mandibles with deciduous processes attached; (C) A. wolcotti, right maxilla, ventral view; (D) A. wolcotti, labial prementum, ventral view. This figure is published in colour in the online version of this journal, which can be accessed via http:// www.brill/ise" ;
